  "id": "azusarealtime",
  "name": "AzusaRealTime",
  "author": "KumaaDeveloper",
  "description": "General",
  "readme_markdown": "## General\nAzusaRealTime is a Pocketmine plug-in that works to always display real-world time on your server.\n\n## Features\n- Can set a country time of interest\n- can change the popup text as desired\n- There are 5 countries available. i.e. Indonesia, Malaysia, Singapore, India, and England.\n  \n## Configuration\n```yaml\n# Configuration for RealTime plugin\n\ntime: idn\npopup-text: \"§eTime: §f{hours}:{minute}:{second}\"\n\n# List of time for each country\n# 'idn' for indonesian\n# 'eng' for England\n# 'ind' for India\n# 'sgp' for Singapore\n# 'mys' for Malaysia\n```",
